sections.heading: Deeds; acknowledgment required
sections.text: The grantor must acknowledge the instrument with an acknowledgment as defined in section 64-205.SourceR.S.1866, c. 43, § 2, p. 280;R.S.1913, § 6197;C.S.1922, § 5596;C.S.1929, § 76-202;R.S.1943, § 76-216;Laws 1978, LB 668, § 1.AnnotationsAcknowledgment must show volunta
